Rotating $360^\circ$ is the same as doing nothing, so rotating $1050^\circ$ is the same as rotating $1050^\circ - 2\cdot 360^\circ = 330^\circ$.  Therefore, we have $\cos 1050^\circ = \cos (1050^\circ - 2\cdot 360^\circ) = \cos 330^\circ$.

