\]Since $\deg d > \deg (4x+1)$ we cannot divide any further. So, $q(x) = 4x^2-1$ and $r(x)=4x+1$. Then
$$q(1)+r(-1) = 4(1)^2+1+4(-1)-1=\boxed{0}.$$

